features: ✅Rear Outlet: The one-piece toilet features a rear outlet design, allowing for easy installation and making it ideal for certain wall-mounted plumbing setups, enhancing the overall functionality of your bathroom. Do not fit bottom oultet. Please realize it before you making purchasing.
✅Sleek Round Shape Bowl: The round shape bowl design of our toilet offers a compact and space-saving solution for smaller bathrooms while providing comfortable seating for users of all ages.
✅Efficient Dual Flush Technology: Allows you to choose between a full or partial flush, providing exceptional water-saving capabilities and reducing your environmental footprint.
✅Quiet and Soft Closing Seat: The soft close toilet seat adds a touch of luxury to your bathroom experience, preventing any sudden slamming and ensuring a quiet and peaceful environment.

✅Comfortable Seating: The higher seat height of 16.5 inches provides a more comfortable seating position for people with mobility issues, elderly individuals, or those who prefer a taller seat. It eases the strain on their knees and makes it easier to sit down and stand up.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: More Features of WinZo WZ5011 Round shaped rear outlet one piece toilet Rear Outlet with one piece toilet This unique rear outlet design allows for the waste to drain horizontally through the back wall rather than the floor drain of most bathrooms.Perfect solution for specific plumbing setups.One piece design, easy to clean and install. High Efficiency Dual Flush Dual flush 1.1 gallons for half flush, 1.6 gallons for full flush which gives the option of less water for liquid waste, more water for solid waste, saving more water than regular single flush. Powerful flushing Wash-down rear discharge toilets designed with extra-large trapway. This allows water to be released from the tank to the bowl very fast, which creates more force and exits through the large trapway just as fast, resulting in a strong flush.
